[18/07/2019 22:45:31] <font color="#ffff00">"La Luna.</font>
[18/07/2019 22:45:35] <font color="#ffff00">Nuestra puerta de entrada</font>
[18/07/2019 22:45:35] <font color="#ffff00">al universo".</font>
